<!-- ═══ ABOUT SNIPPET ══════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="about-snippet" id="about">
    <div class="row g-5 align-items-center">

        <div class="col-lg-6" data-aos="fade-up">
            <span class="section-eyebrow">About me</span>
            <h2 class="section-heading">Quiet until spoken to.<br><em>Bubbly once you do.</em></h2>
            <p class="snippet-body">
                I'm a 28-year-old IT graduate from Nelson Mandela University holding a
                Higher Certificate in IT, a Diploma in Software Development, and an
                <strong>Advanced Diploma in Software Development, which I completed cum laude</strong>.
                Currently finding my voice in the data analytics space as a Digital Analytics
                Intern in Cape Town.
            </p>
            <p class="snippet-body">
                For five years at university I walked in, listened, and walked out.
                My classmates thought I was stuck up. I wasn't, I was just
                <strong>paying attention</strong>. Tech has an unspoken rule that you
                have to be loud to be noticed. I'm learning to work around that,
                one GTM tag at a time.
            </p>
            <p class="snippet-body">
                I'm drawn to work that sits at the intersection of data, tech and
                real problem-solving. I think in systems. I value honesty, kindness
                and curiosity above everything. <strong>Still building. Always curious.</strong>
            </p>

            <div class="snippet-values">
                <span class="snippet-value-chip"> Honesty</span>
                <span class="snippet-value-chip"> Kindness</span>
                <span class="snippet-value-chip"> Joy</span>
                <span class="snippet-value-chip"> Curiosity</span>
            </div>

            <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/ziyanda-mnqwazi-4439782a0"
               target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
               class="snippet-linkedin-link">
                <i class="fab fa-linkedin me-2"></i>
